title: Ep. 157 S&A Investor - CNBC Star Jon Najarian Talks Fiscal Cliff
itunes:title: CNBC Star Jon Najarian Talks Fiscal Cliff
description: Jon Najarian, Fast Money contributor, shows us how to play his favorite stock ideas using option strategies. Aaron Brabham, co-host of the Stansberry Radio, also explains how being drunk is a great reason to change a golf bet.
